name: ParkerUI - Premium Analytics UI kit
description:
ParkerUI is a Premium and High-Quality Analytics Dashboard UI Kit with 15+ high-quality screens and easy to use in Figma. And also we have designed in mobile spot.


The UI Kit is suitable and easy to use for any startups, Agency, beginner and related projects, also the UI Kit is usable for other product designs.


The Parker UI Kit cover all Figma features, including typography, iconography, and with dynamic components & variants.
